reviewText: I plaid the tape twice and it broke II wached the tape twice and when I rewondthe tape it broke at the very end.

The casing on one side was broken.  Many of the skits were ones I had on other video tapes.  The entire tape was quite short.  I love Foster Brooks.  In fact, I was searching for a skit he did with Johnny Carson. . . it was not on this tape.
not one of his best stand ups, got this as a gift but we've seen a lot better out of him, but not all can be great.
